'''Bengel Shipbuiders''' was the manufacturer of various [[Starship/Legends|starships]] and [[Space station/Legends|space stations]], including the [[XQ1 Platform]] and [[XQ2 Platform]]. It was based on [[Ord Thoden]]. They were eventually bought out by the [[Tenloss Syndicate/Legends|Tenloss Corporation]].

